name: XRPN Debuts on Nasdaq as $1B XRP Treasury Strategy Targets Institutional Investors
description: Wet porcelain and brass, the saint begins the rite. One billion units of liquid light are poured onto the parametric altar, anchoring the treasury within the algorithmic sanctum. The regulated exposure is formalized, shimmering under tungsten and teal.
